title: Robotics;Notes - Senomiya Misaki no Mihappyou Shuki
description:
The story detailing the past of Senomiya Misaki, elder sister to the Robotics;Notes heroine Senomiya Akiho.

Adaptation of the [url=https://myanimelist.net/manga/89388]light novel[/url] by the same name.

Part of [url=https://mangadex.com/?page=search&title=Robotic%3BNotes]Robotic;Notes[/url] series.
